<p style="margin:0 0 16px;">
  You have been assigned to copyedit the manuscript
  <strong>{{submissionTitle}}</strong> in Folio.
</p>
{{> folio-email-button href=workbenchUrl label="Open copyediting workbench" align="left"}}
